  "3004590": {
    "name": "Level Up: The Playable Rap Album",
    "steam_appid": 3004590,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/5244422b3299eb068b9e6f62ac62d6eb.webp?t=1730465777\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br><br>Level Up is a dynamic 2D side-scrolling adventure that merges the fun of an 90s side scroller video game with the vibes of a hip-hop album. Created by a multifaceted first time developer — a two-time Ninja Warrior, Nerdcore Rapper, and an Operational Excellence leader — this game is a unique way to experience the hip hop album Level Up featuring the talented artists Substantial, Mega Ran, Kadesh Flow, Mc Ohm-I, and Oso Cinco, with masterful audio engineering by K-Murdock. Brought to life by a successful Kickstarter campaign Level Up promises to bring a new frontier to music experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/25e976a4af88c021d562c7a1566a88d3.poster.avif?t=1730465777\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/25e976a4af88c021d562c7a1566a88d3.webm?t=1730465777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/25e976a4af88c021d562c7a1566a88d3.mp4?t=1730465777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/84a5e9569514c1e84a8935804eecacef.webp?t=1730465777\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br><br>In Level Up, you will traverse through classic 16-bit landscapes where each level unfolds in sync with the tracks from a lyrically masterful album. It's not just about reaching the end, it's about flowing with the beat, becoming one with the music and experiencing music in a new way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/618bce1cf246fa88072919ae57ea48f6.poster.avif?t=1730465777\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/618bce1cf246fa88072919ae57ea48f6.webm?t=1730465777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/618bce1cf246fa88072919ae57ea48f6.mp4?t=1730465777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/4af8deafc9fe74b5be3eccf6192063ef.webp?t=1730465777\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br><br>Unlock songs and get access to game only versions of the album as you progress. Each level introduces a new track, with lyrics that narratively tie into the game’s journey, enhancing the experience and connection between the gameplay and the music.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/7a256aed7a448b84a44d9937a1464904.poster.avif?t=1730465777\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/7a256aed7a448b84a44d9937a1464904.webm?t=1730465777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/7a256aed7a448b84a44d9937a1464904.mp4?t=1730465777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/918263537d13f5a72fd4e668699e3c76.webp?t=1730465777\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br><br>Whether you're in it for the story, the beats, or the challenge, the game meets you where you want by offering:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Story Mode: Play through the album side by side with lyrical mastery.<br></li><li>Freestyle Mode: Play and vibe out to the instrumentals only.<br></li><li>Challenge Mode: Increase the difficulty with stronger enemies and tougher boss battles.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/b70650b57141c238af0d46dfc8e18bac.poster.avif?t=1730465777\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/b70650b57141c238af0d46dfc8e18bac.webm?t=1730465777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/b70650b57141c238af0d46dfc8e18bac.mp4?t=1730465777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/9c4015d0427642dd0942a2193934d7b8.webp?t=1730465777\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br><br>Play through a visually engaging 2D world designed to reflect the ethos of underground hip-hop culture and witness the story unfold through lyrical content.<br>Want to just listen in? Use the in game music player to listen to your favorite tracks. You’ll also receive a copy of the album included with your game download.<br><br>DLC: Explore special content including:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Track breakdowns with the game creator<br></li><li>Insights into the production of both the game and the album through unreleased playtest videos<br></li><li>B-Side versions of the album<br></li><li>Unreleased songs created for the game but never used!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/60775663a463182851c00edb69de0162.poster.avif?t=1730465777\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/60775663a463182851c00edb69de0162.webm?t=1730465777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/60775663a463182851c00edb69de0162.mp4?t=1730465777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/ad2f4ece527a1e6248ea1e3d81b8f57e.webp?t=1730465777\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br><br>Level Up is more than just a game or an album, it’s a multimedia experience that invites players into the heart of hip-hop culture. Share your scores, favorite tracks, and experiences with a vibrant community of gamers and music lovers. <br>Join us on Steam and be a part of the journey to the top. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/d5a03639fc79f34f3f87bf879e487809.poster.avif?t=1730465777\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/d5a03639fc79f34f3f87bf879e487809.webm?t=1730465777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/d5a03639fc79f34f3f87bf879e487809.mp4?t=1730465777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/464906e0f4734ac7db3e9f0a20b6a03f.webp?t=1730465777\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br><br>As a solo developer with a background in high-level athletics and music, the creator of Level Up brings a unique perspective to game development, ensuring that every element of the game resonates with authenticity and high energy. Get ready to Level Up your game, beat by beat.<br><br>                                                  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/c398c3603300706a549a6546a99c41ee.poster.avif?t=1730465777\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/c398c3603300706a549a6546a99c41ee.webm?t=1730465777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004590/extras/c398c3603300706a549a6546a99c41ee.mp4?t=1730465777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
